Summary of activity in 2017

Clanfield operates 5 cameras.

Observations recorded by Clanfield, 2012 to 2017

UKMON data for Clanfield covers the period from 2012 to 2017 and totals 13923 individual meteor observations. These observations comprise 4006 sporadic meteors and 9917 stream meteors.
